<ansi fg="black-bold">.:</ansi> <ansi fg="magenta">Help for </ansi><ansi fg="command">vitality</ansi>

<ansi fg="cyan">Vitality</ansi> measures your physical toughness and endurance. A hardy body
absorbs punishment that would fell a weaker soul.

<ansi fg="yellow">Health</ansi>

* Each point of Vitality adds <ansi fg="cyan">4 maximum HP</ansi>. It is the single most
  important stat for staying alive in a long fight.
* Improves the rate at which you recover health between fights.
</ansi>
